<li><a href="http://bmj.bmjjournals.com/cgi/content/full/319/7208/469" class="external text" title="http://bmj.bmjjournals.com/cgi/content/full/319/7208/469" rel="nofollow">UK hospitals assess eye damage after solar eclipse</a>, British Medical Journal, August 21, 1999, p. 319–469</li>
